snippet.title: Keylocker | Turn Based Cyberpunk Action - Reveal Trailer Remake 4K
snippet.description: This is the trailer for Keylocker, but with graphics in Isometric, that we recently changed. This will probably be the only and last dramatic graphical change we'll go through in graphics. We're completely satisfied now that the game is in isometric!
